      <title>英国金融公司信心遭遇两年来最大跌幅--调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-finance-firms-see-biggest-plunge-sentiment-two-years-survey-2025-01-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工业联合会（CBI）周四发布的一项调查显示，2024年第四季度，英国金融公司商业前景的乐观情绪以两年来最大速度下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-finance-firms-see-biggest-plunge-sentiment-two-years-survey-2025-01-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
