      <title>纽约联储击败波多黎各银行就委内瑞拉相关账户切断提起的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ny-fed-beats-lawsuit-by-puerto-rican-bank-over-venezuela-related-account-cutoff-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，一名美国法官驳回了一家波多黎各银行的诉讼，该银行质疑纽约联邦储备银行为打击与委内瑞拉有联系的银行而决定切断其进入美国中央银行系统的渠道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ny-fed-beats-lawsuit-by-puerto-rican-bank-over-venezuela-related-account-cutoff-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞的利润因投资银行业务的意外之财而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jefferies-profit-more-than-triples-investment-banking-windfall-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融（Jefferies Financial）周三报告称，由于该投资银行从交易咨询中获得了更高的费用且承销活动保持强劲，该公司第四季度的利润增长了两倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jefferies-profit-more-than-triples-investment-banking-windfall-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:23:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，摩根士丹利将 173 名员工晋升为董事总经理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-promotes-173-employees-managing-directors-source-says-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士周三告诉路透社，华尔街巨头摩根士丹利今年将 173 名员工提拔为董事总经理，较 2024 年增长 12%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-promotes-173-employees-managing-directors-source-says-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 20:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通对希腊 Viva Wallet 提起两起诉讼，法律纠纷仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-files-two-lawsuits-against-greeces-viva-wallet-legal-saga-continues-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街银行摩根大通就其对金融科技公司 Viva Wallet 的投资提起了两起诉讼，这是双方围绕如何评估希腊业务的法律纠纷的最新进展。]]></description>
