    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，华平投资集团考虑以 50 多亿美元的价格出售 Modernizing Medicine</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/warburg-pincus-explores-5-billion-plus-sale-modernizing-medicine-sources-say-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，私募股权公司华平投资集团 (Warburg Pincus) 正在考虑收购 Modernizing Medicine (ModMed) 等多种选择，包括出售，此举可能使这家医疗软件提供商的估值超过 50 亿美元（包括债务）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/warburg-pincus-explores-5-billion-plus-sale-modernizing-medicine-sources-say-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 18:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债收益率飙升反映出对更多长期债务的预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/treasury-yield-surge-reflects-expectations-more-long-term-debt-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员表示，长期美国国债收益率已飙升至数月高点，超过短期国债收益率的升幅，部分差异反映出人们预期，即将上任的特朗普政府将需要改变目前对更多依赖短期债务的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/treasury-yield-surge-reflects-expectations-more-long-term-debt-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 17:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
