      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/blockchain-firm-movement-labs-targets-3-billion-valuation-funding-round-source-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士周三透露，Movement Labs 正在进行新一轮融资，融资金额可能达到 1 亿美元，这家区块链开发商的估值将达到 30 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/blockchain-firm-movement-labs-targets-3-billion-valuation-funding-round-source-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:27:12 GMT</pubDate>
