    <item>
      <title>特朗普交易波动之际，欧洲股市受挫吸引投资者回归</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/beaten-down-european-stocks-lure-investors-back-trump-trades-wobble-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对新任总统唐纳德·特朗普上任后美国经济冲击的担忧提升了国际市场的吸引力，受创的欧洲股市在 2024 年创下了相对于华尔街的创纪录表现后，正在吸引投资者回归。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/beaten-down-european-stocks-lure-investors-back-trump-trades-wobble-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
